&lt;p&gt;A 6 month commercial role at the centre of Beauhurst’s expansion into Germany, designed as the launchpad into a permanent commercial career. You’ll support on live deals from day one, contribute directly to how we win the German market, and (if it’s the right fit on both sides) convert into a full-time commercial hire at the end of the internship.&lt;/p&gt;
