&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2010, we work with over 500 organisations across venture capital, major financial institutions, corporates, leading universities, and the Government. We’re not stopping here. We launched in Germany in 2025 as our first step in international expansion, and are now scaling across Europe – Ireland next, then more.&lt;/p&gt;
